        "subject": "LU-2456 lnet: DLC lustre config API Python/C SWIG binding",
        "message": "LU-2456 lnet: DLC lustre config API Python/C SWIG binding\n\nThis is the seventh patch of a set of patches that enables DLC.\n\nThis patch adds Python/C SWIG binding to the Config API.\nIt allows the API to be called from python by first importing\nthe python module created from the library.  This can be used\nby IML to call the configuration API.\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6dc255acfd7d734ca7926aafab603db3fc427d65\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
